# Capacitor's official guidance is to commit the native platform project
# (android/) rather than gitignore it - `cap sync` only updates web assets
# and plugin registrations, not native-side customization (icons,
# permissions, signing config) that Android Studio will end up writing into
# it once this app is developed further. Unlike dist/ (Electron), this
# isn't purely regenerable from config alone.
